author: Aye Yo Jazz
title: Aye Yo Jazz
text: Ordered my wig on Friday and it shipped the next day on Saturday! Email communications and confirmations were extremely fast and all information was included! I recieved my wig on Tuesday! Absolutely loved it! I tried the wig on at my local beauty supply but it was too expensive, at $60 before tax. On Elevate Styles it was $40 including tax AND shipping! I was so excited i literally ordered it while standing in the beauty supply!
